### **4. 26_ChartWaveStream**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes numeric streams as real-time line graphs with smooth animation.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# ChartWaveStream - Realtime Stream Plotter

ChartWaveStream turns live or simulated numerical input into a responsive, auto-scrolling chart.

## Features
- Real-time updates  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Matplotlib-powered  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_ChartWaveStream.git
cd 26_ChartWaveStream
python visualize.py
